> Using Eligibility

# Tests: Edge case expanded tests — generated 2026-03-27

## Test: edg_001 — Zero gross income (client and DOL): exclusion chain clamps to $0; $0 ≤ $1,845 limit — approve

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEdg001:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestEdg001:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $0
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
    -- household_type: A1E
    -- benefit_year: 2026
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $0
    -- gross_earned_income: $0
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Approve)
  assertion (result.reasons = [])
```

## Test: edg_002 — Extreme income — 10× highest limit: client and DOL adjusted $27,320 (A2S 2026 limit=$2,732) — deny (both above standard)

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEdg002:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestEdg002:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $54,725
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
    -- household_type: A2S
    -- benefit_year: 2026
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $164,175
    -- gross_earned_income: $54,725
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Deny)
  assertion (result.reasons = [ IncomeExceedsStandardBoth ])
```

