## Test: edg_005 — All 10 exclusion steps applied: federal ($100), EITC ($50), irregular ($10), student ($200), $20 general, $65 earned, IRWE ($300), one-half, blind work ($200), self-support ($100). Client and DOL adjusted $1,827.50 ≤ $1,845 — approve

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEdg005:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestEdg005:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $5,000
    -- federal_exclusions: $100
    -- eitc_exclusion: $50
    -- irregular_earned_income: $10
    -- student_earned_income: $200
    -- student_monthly_limit: $2,410
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $300
    -- blind_work_expenses: $200
    -- self_support_exclusion: $100
    -- household_type: A1E
    -- benefit_year: 2026
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $15,000
    -- gross_earned_income: $5,000
    -- federal_exclusions: $100
    -- eitc_exclusion: $50
    -- irregular_earned_income: $10
    -- student_earned_income: $200
    -- student_monthly_limit: $2,410
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $300
    -- blind_work_expenses: $200
    -- self_support_exclusion: $100
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Approve)
  assertion (result.reasons = [])
```

